results.name: Möbius transform of sequence A008475.
link: Antti Karttunen, Table of n, a(n) for n = 1..16384
formula: a(n) = 0 if n is 1 or not a power of a prime;
a(n) = n if n is a prime;
a(n) = n*(1 -1/p) if n = p^k, k>= 2, p=prime.
mathematica: f[n_] := Plus @@ Map[Power @@ #1 &, FactorInteger[n]]; mt[n_] := Block[{d = Divisors[n]}, Plus @@ (MoebiusMu /@ (n/d)*f /@ d)]; Table[ mt[n], {n, 93}] (* _Robert G. Wilson v_, Jan 12 2005 *)
